mm, 
<figureCitation id="6186A3FFF27914267613EC5151B12E29" box="[1329,1428,1557,1583]" captionStart="FIGURE 13" captionStartId="17.[151,250,1690,1715]" captionTargetBox="[153,1435,396,1639]" captionTargetId="figure@17.[153,1438,417,1639]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="FIGURE 13. Calvariopsis peruviana sp. nov., male. A) penis; B) apex of penis, lateral view; C) tegmen; D) sternite IX; E) tergite VIII; F) tergite IX; G) tergite VII. Scale bar = 0.25 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2783740/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Fig. 13E</figureCitation>
