<paragraph id="F902BF7AF278142773E5ED6D55BB2F45" blockId="17.[151,1436,1833,2040]" box="[199,414,1833,1859]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Female. Unknown.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F902BF7AF278142773E5ED0A56EB2FB6" blockId="17.[151,1436,1833,2040]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="CBC96368F278142773E5ED0A55DB2F6E" bold="true" box="[199,510,1869,1896]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Measurements and ratios.</emphasis>
Males (n = 10) TL 2.50–3.20 (2.86) mm, PL 0.47–0.67 (0.58) mm, PW 1.13–1.43 (1.32) mm, EL 2.23–2.63 (2.46) mm, EW 1.63–2.07 (1.85) mm, TL/EW 1.50–1.66 (1.55), PW/PL 2.15–2.47 (2.27), EL/EW 1.27–1.40 (1.34), EL/PL 3.80–4.79 (4.25).
</paragraph>
